objects.description: [APT28](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0007) has used built-in tools like ps aux on macOS to determine which processes are running. An [APT28](https://attack.mitre.org/groups/G0007) loader Trojan will enumerate the victim's processes searching for explorer.exe if its current process does not have necessary permissions.
